| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: revenue DESC NULLS FIRST                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |   Projection: hadoop.tpch.nation.n_name, sum(hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_discount) AS revenue                                                                                                          |
|               |     Aggregate: groupBy=[[hadoop.tpch.nation.n_name]], aggr=[[sum(hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * (Float64(1) - hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_discount)) AS sum(hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_discount)]] |
|               |       Projection: hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice, hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_discount, hadoop.tpch.nation.n_name                                                                                                                                  |
|               |         Inner Join: hadoop.tpch.nation.n_regionkey = hadoop.tpch.region.r_regionkey                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |           Projection: hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice, hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_discount, hadoop.tpch.nation.n_name, hadoop.tpch.nation.n_regionkey                                                                                              |
|               |             Inner Join: hadoop.tpch.supplier.s_nationkey = hadoop.tpch.nation.n_nationkey                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |               Projection: hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice, hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_discount, hadoop.tpch.supplier.s_nationkey                                                                                                                   |
|               |                 Inner Join: hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_suppkey = hadoop.tpch.supplier.s_suppkey, hadoop.tpch.customer.c_nationkey = hadoop.tpch.supplier.s_nationkey                                                                                    |
|               |                   Projection: hadoop.tpch.customer.c_nationkey, hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_suppkey, hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice, hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_discount                                                                               |
|               |                     Inner Join: hadoop.tpch.orders.o_orderkey = hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_orderkey                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |                       Projection: hadoop.tpch.customer.c_nationkey, hadoop.tpch.orders.o_orderkey                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |                         Inner Join: hadoop.tpch.customer.c_custkey = hadoop.tpch.orders.o_custkey                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |                           BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |                             TableScan: hadoop.tpch.customer projection=[c_custkey, c_nationkey]                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |                           Projection: hadoop.tpch.orders.o_orderkey, hadoop.tpch.orders.o_custkey                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |                             BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |                               Filter: hadoop.tpch.orders.o_orderdate >= Date32("1994-01-01") AND hadoop.tpch.orders.o_orderdate < Date32("1995-01-01")                                                                                              |
|               |                                 TableScan: hadoop.tpch.orders projection=[o_orderkey, o_custkey, o_orderdate], partial_filters=[hadoop.tpch.orders.o_orderdate >= Date32("1994-01-01"), hadoop.tpch.orders.o_orderdate < Date32("1995-01-01")]      |
|               |                       BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |                         TableScan: hadoop.tpch.lineitem projection=[l_orderkey, l_suppkey, l_extendedprice, l_discount]                                                                                                                             |
|               |                   BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                     TableScan: hadoop.tpch.supplier projection=[s_suppkey, s_nationkey]                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |               BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |                 TableScan: hadoop.tpch.nation projection=[n_nationkey, n_name, n_regionkey]                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |           Projection: hadoop.tpch.region.r_regionkey                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |             BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |               Filter: hadoop.tpch.region.r_name = Utf8("ASIA")                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |                 TableScan: hadoop.tpch.region projection=[r_regionkey, r_name], partial_filters=[hadoop.tpch.region.r_name = Utf8("ASIA")]                                                                                                          |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [revenue@1 DESC]                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |   SortExec: expr=[revenue@1 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[n_name@0 as n_name, sum(hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_discount)@1 as revenue]                                                                                                  |
|               |       AggregateExec: mode=FinalPartitioned, gby=[n_name@0 as n_name], aggr=[sum(hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_discount)]                                                                                 |
|               |         CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |           RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([n_name@0], 16), input_partitions=16                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |             AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[n_name@2 as n_name], aggr=[sum(hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - hadoop.tpch.lineitem.l_discount)]                                                                                    |
|               |               CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |                 HashJoinExec: mode=Partitioned, join_type=Inner, on=[(n_regionkey@3, r_regionkey@0)], projection=[l_extendedprice@0, l_discount@1, n_name@2]                                                                                        |
|               |                   CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |                     RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([n_regionkey@3], 16), input_partitions=16                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |                       CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |                         HashJoinExec: mode=Partitioned, join_type=Inner, on=[(s_nationkey@2, n_nationkey@0)], projection=[l_extendedprice@0, l_discount@1, n_name@4, n_regionkey@5]                                                                 |
|               |                           CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |                             RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([s_nationkey@2], 16), input_partitions=16                                                                                                                                            |
|               |                               CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |                                 HashJoinExec: mode=Partitioned, join_type=Inner, on=[(l_suppkey@1, s_suppkey@0), (c_nationkey@0, s_nationkey@1)], projection=[l_extendedprice@2, l_discount@3, s_nationkey@5]                                       |
|               |                                   CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |                                     RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([l_suppkey@1, c_nationkey@0], 16), input_partitions=16                                                                                                                       |
|               |                                       CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |                                         HashJoinExec: mode=Partitioned, join_type=Inner, on=[(o_orderkey@1, l_orderkey@0)], projection=[c_nationkey@0, l_suppkey@3, l_extendedprice@4, l_discount@5]                                                |
|               |                                           CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |                                             RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([o_orderkey@1], 16), input_partitions=16                                                                                                                             |
|               |                                               CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |                                                 HashJoinExec: mode=Partitioned, join_type=Inner, on=[(c_custkey@0, o_custkey@1)], projection=[c_nationkey@1, o_orderkey@2]                                                                          |
|               |                                                   CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |                                                     RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([c_custkey@0], 16), input_partitions=16                                                                                                                      |
|               |                                                       RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(16), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                         |
|               |                                                         BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |                                                           IcebergTableScan projection:[c_custkey,c_nationkey] predicate:[]                                                                                                                          |
|               |                                                   CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |                                                     RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([o_custkey@1], 16), input_partitions=16                                                                                                                      |
|               |                                                       ProjectionExec: expr=[o_orderkey@0 as o_orderkey, o_custkey@1 as o_custkey]                                                                                                                   |
|               |                                                         BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |                                                           CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                               |
|               |                                                             FilterExec: o_orderdate@2 >= 1994-01-01 AND o_orderdate@2 < 1995-01-01                                                                                                                  |
|               |                                                               RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(16), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                 |
|               |                                                                 IcebergTableScan projection:[o_orderkey,o_custkey,o_orderdate] predicate:[(o_orderdate >= 1994-01-01) AND (o_orderdate < 1995-01-01)]                                               |
|               |                                           CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |                                             RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([l_orderkey@0], 16), input_partitions=16                                                                                                                             |
|               |                                               RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(16), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                 |
|               |                                                 BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |                                                   IcebergTableScan projection:[l_orderkey,l_suppkey,l_extendedprice,l_discount] predicate:[]                                                                                                        |
|               |                                   CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |                                     RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([s_suppkey@0, s_nationkey@1], 16), input_partitions=16                                                                                                                       |
|               |                                       RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(16), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                         |
|               |                                         BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |                                           IcebergTableScan projection:[s_suppkey,s_nationkey] predicate:[]                                                                                                                                          |
