|               |                     RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([r_regionkey@0], 16), input_partitions=16                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |                       ProjectionExec: expr=[r_regionkey@0 as r_regionkey]                                                                                                                                                                           |
